ontent/uploads/2025/06/modern-living-room-300625-357-12-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1667px) 100vw, 1667px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.moynihanben.com/\"\u003eBen Moynihan\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn a kitchen, dark timber joinery wraps the space in warmth, while softly curved cabinetry and brushed gold hardware add a sense of sculptural elegance. A fluted kitchen island with stone benchtop anchors the room, paired with sleek black bar stools that keep the palette grounded.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1478\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-13.jpg\" alt=\"In this kitchen, dark timber joinery wraps the space in warmth, while softly curved cabinetry and brushed gold hardware add a sense of sculptural elegance. A fluted kitchen island with stone benchtop anchors the room, paired with sleek black bar stools that keep the palette grounded.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-13.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-13-940x724.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-13-800x616.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-13-768x591.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-13-1536x1182.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.derekswalwell.com/\"\u003eDerek Swalwell\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1668\" height=\"2500\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-14.jpg\" alt=\"In this kitchen, dark timber joinery wraps the space in warmth, while softly curved cabinetry and brushed gold hardware add a sense of sculptural elegance. A fluted kitchen island with stone benchtop anchors the room, paired with sleek black bar stools that keep the palette grounded.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-14.jpg 1668w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-14-940x1409.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-14-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-14-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-14-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-dark-kitchen-300625-358-14-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1668px) 100vw, 1668px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.derekswalwell.com/\"\u003eDerek Swalwell\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn a bathroom, warm travertine tiles wrap the floor and walls, creating a calm, monolithic backdrop. A fluted black vanity floats effortlessly above the ground, paired with a pale stone benchtop that softens the contrast. Details are restrained but deliberate, from the matte black tapware to the pill-shaped mirror that echoes the project’s sculptural curves.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1667\" height=\"2500\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-bathroom-300625-358-15.jpg\" alt=\"In this bathroom, warm travertine tiles wrap the floor and walls, creating a calm, monolithic backdrop. A fluted black vanity floats effortlessly above the ground, paired with a pale stone benchtop th